even if she's not already dead.

1107
01:13:35,620 --> 01:13:38,415
<i>M. S. One is falling out of the sky, Snow.</i>
<i>You gotta get out.</i>

1108
01:13:38,498 --> 01:13:40,208
<i>- Okay.</i>
<i>- Get to dock 9.</i>

1109
01:13:40,291 --> 01:13:42,293
<i>There's an ORAM engineering suit there.</i>

1110
01:13:42,377 --> 01:13:44,003
<i>Put it on and get outside.</i>

1111
01:13:44,212 --> 01:13:45,296
