1172
01:17:39,405 --> 01:17:40,698
Families!

1173
01:17:42,325 --> 01:17:43,868
Hey, now then, where were we, Smiler?

1174
01:17:49,540 --> 01:17:51,876
<i>Target will be throwing live rounds.</i>

1175
01:17:52,669 --> 01:17:55,880
<i>Watch out, the defense system is still active.</i>

1176
01:18:01,511 --> 01:18:02,762
<i>Okay, here we go.</i>

1177
01:18:04,013 --> 01:18:05,848
<i>Number 5, do you read me?</i>

1178
01:18:11,562 --> 01:18:12,563
<i>We're taking fire. We're taking fire.</i>

1179
