1186
01:18:59,819 --> 01:19:00,862
<i>Coming in low.</i>

1187
01:19:14,500 --> 01:19:16,252
<i>Units two and three, I'm at your left.</i>

1188
01:19:16,502 --> 01:19:19,005
<i>Units two and three, 9 o'clock, 9 o'clock.</i>

1189
01:19:21,340 --> 01:19:24,218
<i>Taking fire, taking fire, unit 11, taking fire.</i>

1190
01:19:24,302 --> 01:19:25,303
