1191
01:19:25,636 --> 01:19:27,096
<i>We got one more to go.</i>

1192
01:19:27,764 --> 01:19:30,016
<i>Unit nine. We're on our way.</i>

1193
01:19:30,767 --> 01:19:32,226
<i>Unit nine, unit nine.</i>

1194
01:19:35,980 --> 01:19:37,440
<i>We're going in, unit 11.</i>

1195
01:19:38,524 --> 01:19:39,859
<i>Go for the tunnel.</i>

1196
01:19:40,568 --> 01:19:41,944
<i>Unit 17, he's on your tail.</i>

1197
01:19:42,278 --> 01:19:43,362
<i>Turn, turn!</i>

1198
01:19:43,529 --> 01:19:44,906
<i>We have you going for the hole, gentlemen.</i>

